Package: petroOne
Type: Package
Title: Create Basic Statistics of Oil and Gas Papers from OnePetro website
Version: 0.1.0.9002
Authors@R: person("Alfonso", "Reyes", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "alfonso.reyes@oilgainsanalytics.com")
Description: Application that retrieves paper information from the OnePetro website.
    Thousand of papers on oil and gas live in OnePetro. By retrieving metadata 
    from the search queries sent to OnePetro a summary of papers that match the
    query words can be retrived to create a dataframe for further analysis. There 
    is some data mining provided with this package such as text cloud.
Depends: R (>= 3.2)    
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
Imports: rvest,
    xml2,
    magrittr, tibble
VignetteBuilder: knitr
